        <para id="id63133">Now, what happens to the surface area if one dimension is multiplied by a constant? For example, how does the surface area change when the height of a rectangular prism is divided by 2?</para>
 <para id="is08324">       <figure id="id63644234"><media id="id63644234_media" alt="">
